title: Taylor Swift becomes first Instagram user to hit 50 million followers
text: Friday, Oct 9 2015, 07:45   Google+ Taylor Swift has become the first person to hit 50 million Instagram followers.The 'Shake it Off' singer said it was clearly because everyone loved seeing pictures of her cats. A photo posted by Taylor Swift (@taylorswift) on Oct 8, 2015 at 2:14pm PDT She wrote: "I'm pretty sure this is just because I have cute cats though."However, her account is usually full of pictures and videos of all her famous buddies joining her on stage during her tour.
